Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.83,0:00:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,L, I want to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.71,0:01:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikoku Wharf,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,an abandoned warehouse\Nknown as the Yellow Box.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How about three days from now,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,on the 28th at 1 p.m.?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Take off everything you're wearing\Nand put it all in that box.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use this blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Miss Takada, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, I did exactly what you told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I made survival my first priority and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Come quickly. Save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.99,0:01:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyomi Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,January 26, 2013,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-2:32 p.m.\N-[loud heartbeat]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Burns to death by setting fire\Nto everything around her,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,including everything she wrote on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It is with great sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that I must announce the passing\Nof one of our very own colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The police have identified\None of the bodies found at the scene
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,as NHN's Ms. Kiyomi Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A two-ton truck and a motorcycle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,were also found in the ruins\Nof the burned-out church.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Investigators suspect\Ngasoline was used to start the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But what I really want to know is\Nwho's gonna be Kira's next spokesperson?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira's message still needs to be spread\Nand someone's gotta do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The death of newscaster Takada\Nwas a horrible tragedy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't help but think\Nthat if she was that careless,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,she couldn't have taken her position\Nas Kira's spokesperson
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It needs to be said:\Nthis is not a woman's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira, please make me\Nyour new representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,KIRA'S KINGDOM
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Give the honor to Sakura TV again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, they just announced her death\Nand already it's started.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Every TV station airing its own segment\Non who should replace her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like she never existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night's judgments\Nunfolded just as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That means Takada and Mikami
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,have had no problems\Ncontacting each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[signal beeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] It's Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hello, L.\N-[Light] Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean to keep bothering you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but with regards to our meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to confirm that we are still set\Nfor the 28th at 1 p.m. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as I predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's sticking with the original time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The 28th, the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] So, the day after tomorrow, huh?\NFinally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Isn't it getting exciting?\N-[Ide] Y-- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but wonder\Nwhat Near wants to show us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuda. Ide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When the day comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a good chance\Nwe might all be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Near] Gevanni.\N-[Gevanni] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Will you be able\Nto make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll be there for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Rester.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Lidner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Gevanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put our best into this, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,JANUARY 28, 2013
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Good morning, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, in regard to Misa Amane,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,we've already set her free.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You may call her to confirm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[beeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] I don't know what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but this must be some sort of\Ncompensation or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They totally put me up\Nin the penthouse suite at the Teito Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this is more like it! [giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. All right, Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stay there\Nfor a little while longer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,until I call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Near.\NI need you to connect me with Mogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the notebook\Nlocked away here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And in order to open the safe\Nit's kept in,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll need the PIN number\Nfrom each member of the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Understood.\NI'll connect you to him immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The number is 62-324.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[keys beeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is my number.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[keys beeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The killer notebook…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"How to use it…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The human whose name is\Nwritten in this notebook shall die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This note will not take effect
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,unless the writer has the person's face\Nin their mind when writing their name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, people sharing\Nthe same name will not be affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If the cause of death is written
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,within 40 seconds of writing\Nthe person's name,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If the cause of death\Nis not specified,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the person will simply die\Nof a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,After writing the cause of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,details of the death should be written\Nin the next six minutes and 40 seconds."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Near, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We've discussed it\Nand it's been decided
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'll be the one\Nto carry the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:07:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,L, are you sure it's all right with you\Nif Mr. Aizawa carries it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose Aizawa for the job\Nbecause we knew you'd prefer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no problems with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] I appreciate it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, we'll see you shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like this is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, more like the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The perfect world of Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And those who know\Nof the notebook’s existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,all of them... will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[car door opens]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake, Near is inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I checked it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[exhaust fan squeaking]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Near, you're far inferior to L.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no right\Nto be wearing a mask of L.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's them. Those four are the SPK.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And the one wearing the mask is Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[grumbles] Hang on. Am I the only one\Nwho sees something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He can go around\Naccusing people of being Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but the fact that he is wearing the mask
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,says he's only trying to protect himself,\Nnot anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] It's just a precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a good possibility\Nthat Kira has already seen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the faces of everyone in this warehouse,\Nexcept for mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, he may be writing down your names\Nas we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'd like to wait for one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, make it 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That should give us\Nmore than enough time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to see if anyone is being controlled\Nbefore they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna wait and see if we die?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not impossible\Nthat Light really is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially since the rest of us\Nare of no use to him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[ticking]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[exhaust fan squeaking]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all just a front\Nto buy some time, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought it would be this hard
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep myself from laughing out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Near must be waiting for him to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all just as I predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[squeaking]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Near! It's already been\Nover 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:12:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nothing's happened yet.\N-[Light] Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because Kira is not here with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone seems to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll remove my mask now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quiet, Near. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still waiting for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an excellent choice of words.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,For the arrival of the one who will\Nsolve everything, once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else is supposed\Nto clear this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] He'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one entrance\Nto this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And the only way to look inside
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is by opening that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That means\Nhe will either through that door,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,or at the very least open it\Nand peek through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And just who is this person anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,X-Kira, the one\Nwho's currently using the notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and killing people on Kira's behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He's bound to come here\Nand bring the notebook with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and then he'll see me\Nand write down my real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, he'll write down\Nthe names of everyone here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,who knows about the notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[all gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't making any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to tell us, Near?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That some other guy\Nis gonna drop by with the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,poke his head in and kill us all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And you want us to sit back\Nand let it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone comes in to the warehouse\Nthrough that door,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,just let him in without resisting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If the door opens slightly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,simply act as if you don't notice\Nanyone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But-- But that's just crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] He's already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-[squeaking becomes louder]\N-[all gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,LIGHT YAGAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mikami] God!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mikami] Delete. Delete. Delete...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-Delete. Delete. Delete. Delete.\N-[rat squeaking]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Delete. Delete. Delete.\NDelete. Delete. Delete!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Delete. Delete. Delete...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! Don't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is fine. You won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] How can you be so sure, Near?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Mikami] Delete. Delete. Delete...\N-Because I modified the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] We took repossession\Nof the notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-and replaced the pages.\N-[Mikami] Delete....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] The person behind the door\Nhas been doing the killings for Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He has also been using\Nexactly one page every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on that, I was able to replace\Nthe page he'd use today,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as all subsequent pages,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,so that no one else would die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mikami] Delete. Delete. Delete.\NDelete. Delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Delete!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[yells] Delete!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] On the other side of that door\Nis X-Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My guess is, in roughly 40 seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll look inside to see if we're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when we'll restrain him\Nand seize the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever's name is not written down,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,must be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira would be the only one\Nthat guy wouldn't try to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[stifles laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I knew it! I knew it! I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew all along\Nyou had tampered with the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Near, you've been completely defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The notebook you altered was nothing more\Nthan a forgery I had Mikami prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the one Mikami's writing their names in,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is the real notebook,\Nwhich had been kept hidden until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing crazily]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I had Mikami\Ncreate a fake notebook for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He also sent Takada several pages\Nfrom the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in fact, it was Takada, not Mikami,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,who was doing the killings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:16:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,As for Mikami,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I had him write names in public\Nseveral times,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,using the fake notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That way he would be noticed\Nby anyone who was following him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But Takada was the one behind the deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikami simply sent the names and faces\Nby cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This little performance was\Nhow I made the SPK believe
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that the Notebook Mikami used\Nwas the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikami's daily behavior is so methodical\Nit's almost obsessive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He always fills exactly one page\Nwith names every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And Near,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you noticed this little habit
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and thought you could use it\Nto tamper with the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All you had to do
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,was count ahead to the page\Nhe'd use on the day of this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you replaced all the pages\Nfrom that day onwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be confident that you\Ncould prevent anyone from dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That was your big plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you couldn't change\Nthe date and time of our meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was one step ahead of you, Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I always knew you were going to try\Nand alter the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I had Mikami\Ncheck the notebook every day
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:17:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,MATSUMOTO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,for signs of tampering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've confirmed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,TO: KIYOMI TAKADA\NI'M DYING TO SEE YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I'd won this game\Nas soon as I got that message.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikami brought a different notebook today,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the real one,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,which had been kept hidden until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, Near,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you did have a chance to win,\Nif only you'd taken it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You were just too naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nothing compared to L.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,L would have considered the possibility\Nof a fake notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,from the very beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And he would have tested it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You had the chance\Nbut you squandered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta say...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so disappointed in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This victory was no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried too hard\Nto win in a noble way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone here dies today,\Nthanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:19:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And as for me,\NI, Kira, will have my perfect victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You there, outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you finished\Nwriting down the names in the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,God!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mikami] Yes, I've written them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[all grunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[stifles laughter]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't laugh yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta hold it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all gonna die 40 seconds\Nafter he wrote down their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty-five seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll claim my victory then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Don't you think it's rather odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he answer you\Nso quickly, calmly and honestly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,when you asked him\Nif he had written down our names yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Who knows? Maybe he's just honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:19:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Or confident that he'll succeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,or perhaps he's seen\Nthrough your brilliant plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Huh? In that case,\Nwe're in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Teru Mikami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not too much trouble for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,won't you please come in\Nand join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know that you're the one
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,who's been judging\Nand executing people for Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've already written down our names
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,then there shouldn't be anything\Nto be afraid of,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you can come right on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Teru Mikami, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's correct.\NThere's no reason to hide from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-You can come in.\N-[men gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,God!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done well, Mikami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How many seconds has it been\Nsince you wrote down the first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,31... 32...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,33… 34…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,35… 36…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,37...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,38!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,39!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Near, looks like I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mikami] Forty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.75,0:21:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]